  "textPreview": "Enroll in our free AI Search Toolkit course and future-proof your search visibility\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nAI Visibility Tracker that fits your delivery map\n\nTrack brands across Google AIOs, AI Mode, ChatGPT, and Gemini, and bring that data to the visibility story your stakeholders are asking for\n\nStart free trial\nRequest a demo\n\nNo credit card required\n\nRun a free AI visibility check against your competitors\nYour domain\nCompetitors\n(up to 5)\nCompetitor #1\nAdd competitor\nAI Engines\nAI Overviews\nAI Mode\nChatGPT\nGemini\nPerplexity\nCheck AI visibility\nYou have 5 free attempts left for today\nThe one powerful toolkit you need for AI search optimization\n\nCrack Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) with real data and actionable insights. Show up where your audience is looking using our leading AI visibility tracker\n\nAI Competitor Research\nAI Results Tracker\nAI Source & Coverage Analysis\nAI Competitor Research\n\nExpand your competitor performance analysis to AI search\n\nMeasure any brand’s overall visibility across AI engines\n\nSee how often AI responses link and mention a specific domain\n\nReview links, mentions, and AI answers for individual prompts\n\nCompare several domains to see gaps in their AI visibility\n\nAccess historical data to monitor dynamics and fluctuations\n\nStart free trial\nTrack your AI visibility in all top answer engines\n\nDiscover how you and your competitors appear in leading LLMs and turn those insights into a solid strategy with the AI visibility tracker\n\nAI Overviews\nChatGPT\nAI Mode\nPerplexity\nGemini\nAI Overviews\n\nGet full visibility into how your brand and competitors appear in Google’s AIOs. Track prompts, analyze links and mentions, compare competitive brands, and monitor LLM brand visibility over time with historical data.\n\nStart free trial\nOptimize for AI search with confidence\n\nUse our new AI search tracker to see how your brand ranks across AI answers. Monitor performance trends with historical insights",
